```plantuml
@startuml thill_kafkacap

participant "Source (Aeron/Multicast/Websocket)" as Source
participant "CaptureDevice" as CaptureDevice
participant "CaptureQueue" as CaptureQueue
participant "Deduplicator" as Deduplicator
participant "Kafka Topic (Capture)" as KafkaCapture
participant "Kafka Topic (Outbound)" as KafkaOutbound

Source -> CaptureDevice : Message
CaptureDevice -> CaptureQueue : Buffer message
CaptureQueue -> KafkaCapture : Publish to capture topic
KafkaCapture -> Deduplicator : Consume messages
Deduplicator -> Deduplicator : Deduplicate messages
Deduplicator -> KafkaOutbound : Publish unique messages

@enduml
```